            <div type="edition">
            <ab>
                <lb n="1"/>D<hi rend="tall">i</hi>s Manibus
                <lb n="2"/><persName><name type="praenomen" key="Marcus"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan></name> <name type="gentilicium" key="Manneius">Mannei</name> <name type="cognomen" key="Amphion">Amphioni<unclear>s</unclear>.</name></persName>
                <lb n="3"/><persName><name type="praenomen" key="Marcus"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan></name> <name type="gentilicium" key="Manneius">Manneius</name> <name type="cognomen" key="Zethus">Zethu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied></name></persName>
                <lb n="4"/>frater gemin<unclear>o</unclear>
                <lb n="5"/>carissimo
                <lb n="6"/>bene merenti <supplied reason="undefined" evidence="previouseditor">et</supplied>
                <lb n="7"/><persName><name type="gentilicium" key="Manneia">Manneia</name> <name type="cognomen" key="Lamyra">Lamyr<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied></name></persName>
                <lb n="8"/>patrono optimo et
                <lb n="9"/>dignissimo
                <lb n="10"/>fecerunt. 
            </ab></div>
            
            <div type="translation">
                <p>To the divine spirits of Marcus Manneius Amphion. His brother Marcus Manneius Zethus and Manneia Lamyra made (this) for his dearest and well-deserving twin and for her best and most worthy patron.</p>
                </div>

            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Line 1: Long <hi rend="italic">I</hi> in <hi rend="italic">Dis</hi>. De Rossi does not record interpunct between these words.</p>
                <p>Line 3: De Rossi records the symbols here, but reverses their correct sides, with patera on left and urceus on right.</p>
                <p>Line 4: <hi rend="italic"><unclear>Z</unclear>ethus</hi> Vison√†. De Rossi does not record interpunct between these words.</p>
                <p>Line 6: <hi rend="italic">benemerenti et</hi> De Rossi.</p>
                <p>Line 7: <hi rend="italic">Lamyra</hi> Vison√† and De Rossi.</p>
                <p>Line 10: Spacing inconsistent; it appears carver attempted to maintain centered position of <hi rend="italic">fecerunt</hi> by shrinking the spaces between later letters.</p>
                <p>Interpuncts between words, excluding <hi rend="italic">bene merenti</hi> line 6 and <hi rend="italic">patrono optimo</hi> line 8.</p></div>
            

